        "created_at": "2016-06-07T20:33:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><span alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"broken-image\" title=\"This image is broken\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-unlink svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#unlink\"></use></svg></span><br>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>2014 Domaine Ramonet Saint-Aubin 1er Cru Les Murgers des Dents de Chien</strong> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Saint-Aubin 1er Cru (6/7/2016)</em><br>\nDiscreet elegant nose. Has finesse rather than weight with excellent mineral precision, refined citrus and balancing acidity. Spicy and intense on the finish \u2026</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
